<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 هيا رنموا معنا اهتفوا لربنا
 فهو مستحق الحمدل أعطوا له كل المجد
 مجدًا في الأعالي مجدًا
 1- angels we have heard on high
 Sweetly singing o'er the plains
 And the mountains in reply
 Echo back their joyous strains
 Gloria Gloria in excelsis deo
 2- come to Bethlehem and see
 Him whose birth the angels sing
 Come adore on bended knee
 Chirst the lord the newborn king
 Gloria Gloria in excelsis Deo
 Gloria still we sing
 Gloria unto our king
 Gloria Gloria Gloria</lyrics>
<title>مجدًا في الأعالي</title>
<hymn_number>7139</hymn_number>
</song>